metadata.name: HOLLYWOOD Dystopian
metadata.description:
This work represents the changing of guards from the closed exclusive membership of Old Hollywood values and traditions to a New Day in LA.  

The digital world its leading the charge.  Expanding the mindset of the old regime to the brand new world of streaming, diversity,  inclusion and equity for all.  

Times have changed in arts and entertainment.

Created for the Mr.  Augmented AR Exhibition under the theme 'DYSTOPIAN Los Angeles" April 16 2022.
